collections::​deque
uvm_pkg.​uvm_queue​#(T)
collections::​ .​sequential_collection​#(T)
collections::​ .​deque​#(type T=uvm_object)

An impelmentation of a deque.

Similar to <uvm_queue> with the same general idea of the ability to pass around a systemverilog queue as an object reference without the copy overhead but provides further utilities for accessing and iterating the collection.

index
virtual function int index(
T 
item
)

Find the index of the first occurence of an item in the collection.

implementations should return a zero-based index of the first item whose value is equal to _item.

implementations should return -1 to indicate that _item could not be found and is not a part of the collection.
